  "design_reference": "docs/design/10-writer-calc.md (Writer sidebar rail/decks; Page style and Navigator panels) -- cited by title/purpose.",
  "note": "WIN-WR-004. Composition-pinning triad for the two real, non-experimental Writer-owned sidebar decks that SwPanelFactory routes to production panel classes: the WriterPageDeck 'Styles' panel (PageStylesPanel over pagestylespanel.ui) and the NavigatorDeck panel (SwNavigationPI over navigatorpanel.ui). For each surface this contract pins, fail-closed: (a) every real .ui widget id the .cxx binds via m_xBuilder->weld_*(id) exists in the .ui with the matching GtkBuilder class; (b) SwPanelFactory.cxx still routes the ImplementationURL suffix to the real Create() call; (c) the one load-bearing mutually-exclusive visibility state machine each panel owns is intact as source code, extracted by brace-matched per-branch bodies -- PageStylesPanel::Update()'s switch(eXFS) over {NONE,SOLID,GRADIENT,HATCH,BITMAP/PATTERN} (GRADIENT is the real two-visible case: mxBgColorLB AND mxBgGradientLB both shown) plus the post-switch TriggerDeckLayouting() relayout; and SwNavigationPI::ToggleTree()'s global-vs-content mode branches (show/hide sets + SetGlobalMode(bool)). This asserts NO new definition.xml part/state: the controls (combobox, ColorListBox/menu-button, toolbar, treeview) are stock weld widgets already covered by generic control theming outside this row's scope. The SwNavigationPI::ToggleTree LOK early-return path (comphelper::LibreOfficeKit::isActive() -> HideTree + return) is deliberately OUT of scope and recorded as a carve-out, not pinned. runtime_verified is false throughout: no native build, deck pixels, or runtime interaction are claimed. Experimental SwStylePresetsPanel/SwThemePanel (SwDesignDeck, IsExperimental=true) are excluded; cross-app Properties-deck panels (ParaPropertyPanel/TextPropertyPanel live in svx via SvxPanelFactory) are not sw-owned and excluded.",
  "expected_surfaces": 2,
  "surfaces": [
    {
      "surface_id": "writer.sidebar.page-styles",
      "title": "WriterPageDeck Styles panel (PageStylesPanel background-fill switch)",
      "status": "source-declared",
      "runtime_verified": false,
      "owner_sources": [
        "sw/source/uibase/sidebar/PageStylesPanel.cxx",
        "sw/source/uibase/sidebar/PageStylesPanel.hxx"
      ],
      "ui_file": "sw/uiconfig/swriter/ui/pagestylespanel.ui",
      "widget_source": "sw/source/uibase/sidebar/PageStylesPanel.cxx",
      "widget_bindings": [
        {"id": "lbcolor", "gtk_class": "GtkMenuButton", "weld_accessor": "weld_menu_button"},
        {"id": "lbhatching", "gtk_class": "GtkComboBox", "weld_accessor": "weld_combo_box"},
        {"id": "lbgradient", "gtk_class": "GtkMenuButton", "weld_accessor": "weld_menu_button"},
        {"id": "lbbitmap", "gtk_class": "GtkComboBox", "weld_accessor": "weld_combo_box"},
        {"id": "layoutbox", "gtk_class": "GtkComboBoxText", "weld_accessor": "weld_combo_box"},
        {"id": "columnbox", "gtk_class": "GtkComboBoxText", "weld_accessor": "weld_combo_box"},
        {"id": "numberbox", "gtk_class": "GtkComboBoxText", "weld_accessor": "weld_combo_box"},
        {"id": "bgselect", "gtk_class": "GtkComboBoxText", "weld_accessor": "weld_combo_box"},
        {"id": "customlabel", "gtk_class": "GtkLabel", "weld_accessor": "weld_label"}
      ],
      "factory_routing": {
        "source": "sw/source/uibase/sidebar/SwPanelFactory.cxx",
        "resource_suffix": "/PageStylesPanel",
        "create_call": "PageStylesPanel::Create"
      },
      "visibility_switch": {
        "source": "sw/source/uibase/sidebar/PageStylesPanel.cxx",
        "function_signature": "PageStylesPanel::Update(",
        "method_side_effects": ["m_pPanel->TriggerDeckLayouting()"],
        "branches": [
          {"name": "NONE", "anchor": "case NONE:", "shown": [], "hidden": ["mxBgColorLB", "mxBgHatchingLB", "mxBgGradientLB", "mxBgBitmapLB"]},
          {"name": "SOLID", "anchor": "case SOLID:", "shown": ["mxBgColorLB"], "hidden": ["mxBgBitmapLB", "mxBgGradientLB", "mxBgHatchingLB"]},
          {"name": "GRADIENT", "anchor": "case GRADIENT:", "shown": ["mxBgColorLB", "mxBgGradientLB"], "hidden": ["mxBgBitmapLB", "mxBgHatchingLB"]},
          {"name": "HATCH", "anchor": "case HATCH:", "shown": ["mxBgHatchingLB"], "hidden": ["mxBgColorLB", "mxBgGradientLB", "mxBgBitmapLB"]},
          {"name": "BITMAP-PATTERN", "anchor": "case BITMAP:", "shown": ["mxBgBitmapLB"], "hidden": ["mxBgColorLB", "mxBgGradientLB", "mxBgHatchingLB"]}
        ]
      }
    },
